}

' ─── 调用链 ───

Transport --> Guard : deny external check\n(EXTERNAL_CALLER_ALLOWED.hand_off_session = false)
Guard --> Handler : HandOffSessionArgs

' caller cwd 反查
Handler --> ResolveCwd : callerSid
ResolveCwd --> SessionRepo : sessionRepo.get(callerSid)
SessionRepo --> DB : SELECT cwd, cwdReleaseMarker
Handler --> MergeCwd : merge implDeps

' 双模式分流
alt plan-driven (plan_id 传)
  Handler --> Impl : handOffSessionImpl({planId, planFilePathOverride?, phaseLabel?})
  Impl --> PlansLocal : fallback chain step 1
  Impl --> PlansRef : fallback chain step 2
  Impl --> PlansHome : fallback chain step 3
  Impl ..> Worktree : 校验 worktree_path 字段存在
  Impl --> Handler : { planFilePath, worktreePath, mainRepo, coldStartPrompt }
else generic (无 plan_id)
  Handler --> Handler : 直接组装 generic 上下文\n(不调 impl)
end

' spawn 新 SDK session
Handler --> Spawn : spawnSessionHandler({adapter, cwd, prompt, handOffMode: true, extra_allow_write?})
Spawn --> ClaudeAdapter : createSession (adapter='claude-code')
Spawn --> CodexAdapter : createSession (adapter='codex-cli')
ClaudeAdapter --> SDKProc : claude SDK subprocess
CodexAdapter --> SDKProc : codex SDK subprocess
SDKProc --> SessionRepo : sessionRepo.upsert(newSid, ...)
Spawn --> Handler : { sessionId: newSid, teamId?, spawnPromptMessageId? }

' phase 1.5 adopt (optional)
Handler --> TeamRepo : agentDeckTeamRepo.swapLead(teamId, callerSid, newSid) (per team loop)
TeamRepo --> DB : UPDATE team_members SET role='lead' WHERE session_id=newSid
Handler --> AdoptCtx : buildAdoptedTeamsContextBlock(adopted) → 注入 spawn prompt 顶部

' phase 1.6 task reassign (三态)
Handler --> TaskRepo : reassignTaskOwner / applyHandOffSkipPolicy (按 team_task_policy)
TaskRepo --> DB : UPDATE / DELETE tasks (per policy)

' phase 2 cleanup
Handler --> Baton : runBatonCleanup({callerSid, toolName})
Baton --> Shutdown : phase 1 (adopt=true 时 skip)
Shutdown --> TeamRepo : listActiveMembersByTeam
Shutdown --> SM : sessionManager.close(teammateSid) excludeSessionIds={newSid}
SM --> EventBus : emit 'session-status-changed'

Baton --> ArchiveCaller : phase 2 (archive_caller=false 时 skip)
ArchiveCaller --> SessionRepo : sessionRepo.archive(callerSid)
ArchiveCaller --> EventBus : emit 'session-status-changed' (caller archived)

Baton --> Handler : { teammatesShutdown, archived }
Handler --> Transport : ok({mode, sessionId, archived, taskReassignment, adopted?, ...})

@enduml
